#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "User support, fixing bugs, and improving the stability of the app are our top priority. The list of requests and bug reports grows every day, and there are many support requests to respond to on the App Store, Google Play, and support emails."
