#, no-wrap
msgid "The Organic Maps project & company were founded, based on the Maps.Me source code."
msgstr "An ragdres ha kompani Organic Maps o selys, selys war'n kod Maps.Me."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Governance issues and community concerns not addressed by company shareholders stalled the development of Organic Maps for months."
msgstr "Kudynnow governieth ha bernyow kemeneth ny kewsel orth gans kevranoryon hedhys an displegyans dres misyow."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
